Better Females - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2812
No More Blocky Faces - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=30
High Quality Eyes - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=498
Detailed Lips - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=689
AOF Believable Hair - http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4307

She\'s kinda mage and one handed hybrid but mostly one handed. 
Other infos:
-Unique items: Sanguine Rose, Ebony Mail, Dawnbreaker, Mace of Molag Bal, Wabbajack, Archmage\'s Robe, Staff of Magnus
-Conjures: Familiar, Flame, Frost, Storm
